typedFirst, typedLast: attributes (& fields) you can write and read
prettyFirst, prettyLast, prettyFull: pretty-printed fields you may only read.
Don't write to the pretty* fields.

Sanitizing is:
Removing leading and trailing whitespace.
Converting on or more whitespace chars to a single space.

